As a user, I wish I could post objects that I found and their location to alert their owner. 

As a user, I wish I could post objects that I lost and their likely location to alert others to look for my item.

As an administrator, I wish I could ban users that falsely claim items that are not theirs are theirs. 

As a user, I wish I could offer rewards and incentizes for other users who found my items. 
